        entry
          definition "A flexible, slender twig or shoot, especially when used as a band or for binding; a withy."
        entry
          definition "A band of twisted twigs."
        entry
          definition "An elastic handle to a tool to save the hand from the shock of blows."
        entry
          definition "An iron attachment on one end of a mast or boom, with a ring, through which another mast or boom is rigged out and secured."
        entry
          definition "A partition between flues in a chimney."
